Change log for v0.4.0-rc2
================================

 - (Added) ListBoxBindings & ListBoxAdapter
 - (Bug Fix) Various ListBox/ListModel synchronization bugs
 - (Added) History support in application module
 - (Added) AbsoluteLayout demo
 - (Update) AbsoluteLayout
 - (Refactor) MosaicBindings to GWTMosaicBindings
 - (Bug Fix) Bug in LayoutPanel onAttach()/onDetach() for DecoratorPanel fixed
 - (Upgrade) gwt-beans-binding 0.3
 - (Bug Fix) BoxLayout bad center/end alignments with DecoratorPanel fixed & code simplified
 - (Added) UiBinder ColumnLayout, RowLayout, GridLayout & FlowLayout changes to support the LayoutPanel UiBinder parser & Showcase demos
 - (Added) UiBinder support for LayoutPanel. FillLayout, BorderLayout & BoxLayout changes to support the LayoutPanel UiBinder parser & Showcase demos
 - (Added) FlowLayout and Showcase demo
 - (Bug Fix) fix the layout issue after the scrollbar appears/dissapears for the first time
 - (Bug Fix) LiveTable scrollbar synchronization fixed
 - (Added) LiveTableColumnViewItem.getColumnView() added
 - (Update) CSS for form separator (text color set to #5a5a5a) and scroll tables data wrapper (background-color: white)
 - (Bug Fix) Loading panel animation removed
 - (Update) Column/RowLayout splitbar CSS for aegean theme & code cleanup
 - (Added) ColumnView.deleteColumn(int index) & LiveTableColumnViewItem.
 - (Added) class SerializableResponse that extends com.google.gwt.gen2.table.client.TableModelHelper.SerializableResponse and adds rowCount property.

Change log for v0.4.0-rc1
================================
 - (Added) ColumnLayout, RowLayout and ColumnView widget + 2 demos
 - (Added) HasLayoutManager.needsLayout() & required cahnges
 - (Update) ColumnLayout functionality completed & BoxLayout code cleanup
 - (Bug Fix) LazyLayoutPanel layout problems fix
 - (Bug Fix) ScrollLayoutPanel.ensureVisibleImpl() scrolls also in horizontal direction
 - (Added) Individual widget invalidation
 - (Bug Fix) Various TabLayoutPanel bugs fixed
 - (Buf Fix) Don't cache percentage values in size (new layout system size cache)
 - (Added) Similar size cache and size calculations with Forms module
 - (Bug Fix) BorderLayout collapsed status NPE fixed
 - (Added) BorderLayout support for custom widgets in collapsed status
 - (Added) AnimationCallback in LayoutPanel & StackLayoutPanel z-index bug fixed.
 - (Update) Layout management improvements, transition animations for FillLayout, BoxLayout, GridLayout & BorderLayout, Showcase demo application update
 - (Upgrade) gwt-beans-binding-3.0.0, gwt-dnd-3.0.0, gwt-incubator-trunk-r1738 from gwt-beans-binding-0.2.4, gwt-dnd-2.6.5, gwt-incubator-trunk-r1684
 - (Added) BoxLayout transition animation and optimizations, cloneNode() is used in getPreferredSize().
 - (Cleanup) ToolButton
 - (Update) DecoratedLayoutPanel respects size if added to a normal GWT Panel
 - (Update) LayoutPanel respects size if added to a normal GWT Panel
 - (Cleanup) Viewport all @Deprecated methods removed

